OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,FThe chairman of the public inquiry
OL,7,Finto the Southport attack has promised
OL,8,Fto do everything "humanly possible" to
OL,9,Fanswer the questions of bereaved
OL,10,Ffamilies and victims.
OL,12,FAddressing the inquiry the day after
OL,13,Fit heard from the families of Elsie
OL,14,FDot Stancombe, seven, Bebe King, six,
OL,15,Fand Alice da Silva Aguiar, nine, who
OL,16,Fwere murdered as they attended a
OL,17,FTaylor Swift dance class, Sir Adrian
OL,18,FFulford praised the "the courage and
OL,19,Fdignity" who had already given
OL,20,Fevidence.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@cO]
