OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,FThe inquiry aims at Liverpool Town
OL,7,FHall aims to examine Axel Rudakubana's
OL,8,Fdealings with relevant agencies before
OL,9,Fhe carried out his violent attack on
OL,10,F29 July 2024.
OL,12,FImpact evidence has also been heard
OL,13,Ffrom families of the other children
OL,14,Fpresent on the day, businessman
OL,15,FJonathan Hayes, who was injured in the
OL,16,Fattack, and teachers Leanne Lucas and
OL,17,FHeidi Liddle, who were running the
OL,18,Fclass.
