OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,FSir Adrian said: "None of us who have
OL,7,Fbeen present in this chamber will ever
OL,8,Fforget what we have heard, along with
OL,9,Fthe courage and dignity of each and
OL,10,Fevery one of those who have spoken or
OL,11,Fwho have provided silent support.
OL,13,F"Those statements and portraits
OL,14,Fexplain and define why this inquiry is
OL,15,Fbeing conducted."
