OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,FHe said the "incalculable loss and
OL,7,Fharm" which had been "vividly
OL,8,Fdescribed" in the impact evidence made
OL,9,Fit necessary to to investigate what
OL,10,Fhappened in the years leading up to
OL,11,Fthe attack.
OL,13,FHe added: "I am acutely aware that the
OL,14,Ffamilies and the victims expect the
OL,15,Ffullest explanation of how it was
OL,16,Fpossible for something so appalling to
OL,17,Fhave happened, following what I intend
OL,18,Fwill be rigorous and fair scrutiny of
OL,19,Fevery relevant stage leading up to
OL,20,FJuly 29 2024.
OL,26,@nD@MOUoD@EO]oD@VOUpD@JO]uD@KOU
