OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,F"What occurred on that day has made it
OL,7,Fcritically necessary, moreover, to
OL,8,Fidentify all the changes that need to
OL,9,Fbe implemented in order to ensure, as
OL,10,Fbest as our society is able, that
OL,11,Fthere is no repetition.
OL,13,F"I would therefore reassure families
OL,14,Fand the victims, given we are now
OL,15,Fturning to the opening statements and
OL,16,Fevidence, that I and the inquiry team,
OL,17,Fwith the necessary assistance of all
OL,18,Fagencies, bodies and individuals whose
OL,19,Factions will be scrutinised, will do
OL,20,Feverything that's humanly possible to
OL,21,Fanswer those questions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
