OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,F"Our task over the coming weeks is to
OL,7,Fprovide explanations and to ensure to
OL,8,Fthe fullest extent possible that
OL,9,Flessons are learnt and recommendations
OL,10,Fare made as to all the areas where
OL,11,Fthings urgently need to be done
OL,12,Fdifferently."
