OL,3,CChairman will do 'everything possible'
OL,4,Cto answer Southport families' questions
OL,6,FIn his opening statement, counsel to
OL,7,Fthe Southport Inquiry Nicholas Moss KC
OL,8,Fsaid the inquiry would establish a
OL,9,Fdefinitive account of the attack as
OL,10,Fwell as relevant events leading up to
OL,11,Fit, including a timeline of the
OL,12,Fattacker's history and "interactions
OL,13,Fwith various state systems including
OL,14,Fcriminal justice, education, social
OL,15,Fcare and healthcare".
OL,17,FHe told the inquiry: "The clear and
OL,18,Fdirect responsibility for the attack
OL,19,Fis the egregious criminal conduct of
OL,20,FAR himself.
OL,26,@tD@XOUwD@TO]
